title: Looking for Mid laner for Ranked 5's
body:
So yea, looking for a mid laner to fill the team.
We're not pro's, but we understand a half decent amount about the game and we're just looking to improve and rank up. Just generally get better together.

Current Line up is ;

Top: Plat 5
Jg: G4
Adc: G5
Supp:G3

We're going to be looking to stick to a schedule. Four nights a week. Which is as follows.

Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday - 8pm
Sunday - 9pm

So yea, if this takes to your liking, times and what not suit you, shoot me a message online.

IGN: TheLivingEnd
